# Git mailmap — canonicalizes author/committer identity for display.
#
# Format: <canonical-email> <commit-email>
# (See `git help mailmap` for full syntax.)
#
# Tools that respect .mailmap include: `git log`, `git shortlog`, `git blame`,
# and GitHub's commit UI. Raw git data (individual commit objects) is
# unchanged — the mapping is applied at display time only.

<contact@getnaqi.com> <gorthidz@gmail.com>
